Community development and contribution
As more OWLs are built and fallow weed control systems developed, we would love to
share the end results here. Please get in contact and we can upload images of the finished
systems on this page.
OWL now has a Discussion page too. Use this for any ideas, suggestions, comments,
completed units or other points you'd like to raise. If there's a bug or improvement, please
raise an issue.
Please review the contribution page for all the details on how to contribute and follow
community guidelines.Hardware Requirements
